// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3887 — Mass File Rename (qilin)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cdb3cb9b-b800-5369-9790-16219128ad18

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
